thm pm11.57(setvar s0, setvar s1, wff w0) {
  |- wb(wal(s0, w0), wal(s0, wal(s1, wa(w0, wsb(s1, s0, w0)))))
  -| diffsw(s1, w0)
} = {
  impbii(wal(s0, w0), wal(s0, wal(s1, wa(w0, wsb(s1, s0, w0)))))
  axc4i(s0, w0, wal(s1, wa(w0, wsb(s1, s0, w0))))
  alrimi(s1, wal(s0, w0), wa(w0, wsb(s1, s0, w0)))
  nfal(s1, s0, w0)
  nfv(s1, w0)
  jca(wal(s0, w0), w0, wsb(s1, s0, w0))
  sp(s0, w0)
  stdpc4(s0, s1, w0)
  alimi(s0, wal(s1, wa(w0, wsb(s1, s0, w0))), w0)
  sps(s1, wa(w0, wsb(s1, s0, w0)), w0)
  simpl(w0, wsb(s1, s0, w0))
}

thm pm11.59(setvar s0, setvar s1, wff w0, wff w1) {

  alrimi(s1, wal(s0, wi(w0, w1)), wal(s0, wi(wa(w0, wsb(s1, s0, w0)), wa(w1, wsb(s1, s0, w1)))))
  nfal(s1, s0, wi(w0, w1))
  nfv(s1, wi(w0, w1))
  axc4i(s0, wi(w0, w1), wi(wa(w0, wsb(s1, s0, w0)), wa(w1, wsb(s1, s0, w1))))
  anim12d(wal(s0, wi(w0, w1)), w0, wsb(s1, s0, w0), w1, wsb(s1, s0, w1))
  sp(s0, wi(w0, w1))
  spsbim(s0, s1, w0, w1)
  diff.wi.s(s1, w0, w1)
}

  adantl(wex(s0, w0), wex(s1, w1), wi(wal(s0, wal(s1, wi(wa(w0, w1), wa(w2, w3)))), wal(s0, wi(w0, w2))))

  3imtr3g(wal(s1, wi(wa(w0, w1), wa(w2, w3))), wa(w0, wex(s1, w1)), wa(w2, wex(s1, w3)), wex(s1, wa(w0, w1)), wex(s1, wa(w2, w3)))

  adantr(wex(s0, w0), wex(s1, w1), wi(wal(s0, wal(s1, wi(wa(w0, w1), wa(w2, w3)))), wal(s1, wi(w1, w3))))
  syl5(wex(s0, w0), wal(s0, wal(s1, wi(wa(w0, w1), wa(w2, w3)))), wal(s1, wi(w1, w3)), wal(s1, wal(s0, wi(wa(w0, w1), wa(w2, w3)))))
  ax-11(s0, s1, wi(wa(w0, w1), wa(w2, w3)))
  alimd(s1, wex(s0, w0), wal(s0, wi(wa(w0, w1), wa(w2, w3))), wi(w1, w3))
  nfex(s1, s0, w0)
  nfv(s1, w0)

  3imtr3g(wal(s0, wi(wa(w0, w1), wa(w2, w3))), wa(wex(s0, w0), w1), wa(wex(s0, w2), w3), wex(s0, wa(w0, w1)), wex(s0, wa(w2, w3)))
